                                      cog

cog is a dead-simple script that installs AUR packages

Why?
-----

Existing AUR helpers try to reinvent the wheel. This is an attempt to create a
small script that leverages existing tools to install packages.

depends
-------

- cower (https://github.com/falconindy/cower)

setup
-----

- Clone this repo
- Copy the file 'cogrc' to ~/.config/cogrc
- Edit ~/.config/cogrc
- Symlink cog to somewhere in your path

Usage
-----

usage: cog <package>

  options
    -f, --force   overwrite existing files when downloading
                    (passed to cower)

